{"tid":2017112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞開行上調疫情對全球經濟損失預測 或達8.8萬億元","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T02:05:01.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e02757744219c0020ddd76af44bf6757ccde4a","tid":2017112,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"亞開行上調疫情對全球經濟損失預測 或達8.8萬億元<br />\n2020-05-15 HKT 09:17<br />\n<br />\n亞洲開發銀行表示，今年全球因新型肺炎疫情造成的經濟損失，可能介乎5.8至8.8萬億美元，較早前估計增加逾1倍，相當於全球國內生產總值的6.4%至9.7%，主要是防疫採取的封鎖措施癱瘓經濟。<br />\n<br />\n亞開行估計，疫情導致亞洲造成的經濟損失介乎1.7至2.5萬億美元之間。<br />\n<br />\n首席經濟學家澤田康幸指出，新的分析反映出疫情可能造成極重大經濟影響的前景，亦顯示出政策干預或可發揮重要作用，幫助降低經濟損失。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526269-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526269-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=e4720b83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526269-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d405e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526269-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fc4079fda908b81b3810153f80bf26ccf94abe06","tid":2017112,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"樓價仲爆升"},{"pid":"fc71ef748c9ec65d4ac5c1e7bbf68eddc10d3916","tid":2017112,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."}]}